value.name: A Super Epic Tad­pole Jour­ney to the Sur­face of Croak Creek
value.original_name: A Super Epic Tad­pole Jour­ney to the Sur­face of Croak Creek
value.overview: Two sibling tadpoles Ted and Paula, take on the dangers of the river to join their frog family on the surface. Regular reminders of how far they are from the surface emphasize the verticality of their journey as encounters with predators and other foes threaten their progress.
